com.android.volley

Class AsyncNetwork

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.volley.AsyncNetwork
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Network
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicAsyncNetwork

    public abstract class AsyncNetwork
extends java.lang.Object
implements Network
    An asynchronous implementation of Network to perform requests.

    WARNING: This API is experimental and subject to breaking changes. Please see https://github.com/google/volley/wiki/Asynchronous-Volley for more details.
